quite easily, I believe.

291
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:52,320
There are access tunnels
that nobody knows about.

292
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,760
Access tunnels?

293
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:55,640
Sit down. Come here.

294
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:58,560
Thank you, sir. A great honor indeed.

295
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:00,960
What's your name again?

296
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,160
Everyone here calls me Penguin, sir.

297
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,280
You don't like that name, huh?

298
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,160
Yeah, well, you're wrong.

299
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:10,080
It's a good name.

300
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,880
Works for you.

301
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:16,160
So, how do you know this man?
The janitor?

302
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,280
I have connections.

303
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,160
