304
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,320
I think I can persuade him to be.

305
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:24,560
Boss, this guy is a dishwasher
in a suit...

306
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:25,640
Relax.

307
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:27,800
Is that right, Penguin?

308
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:30,000
Are you just a dishwasher?

309
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:32,600
'Cause I don't get that vibe.

310
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,160
