313
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,480
I guess that's why you're the don.

314
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,560
Well...

315
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,320
I'm not a dishwasher.

316
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:49,440
