so to speak.

317
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,320
So, you've rode some bulls, huh?

318
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,480
- Well...
- I knew it.

319
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:56,240
Well, tell all, cowboy.

320
00:18:57,560 --> 00:19:00,400
Well, my real name
is Oswald Cobblepot.

321
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:03,120
And I think that once you hear
my story,

322
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,440
you'll agree that I could be
a great asset for you, sir.

323
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:08,760
It's a long, funny story really.

324
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:11,640
But the headline,
just so you're not surprised...

325
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:14,800
I used to work for Fish Mooney.

326
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:15,880
Fish Mooney?

327
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:17,760
- Hey.
- Yes, sir.

328
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:20,640
I was privy to many aspects
of the Falcone family business.

329
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:23,360
- Until they tried to kill me.
- Yeah.

330
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,160
Hello.

331
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,240
Suffice it to say...

332
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:31,200
That is a funny story.

333
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:46,800
I'm Taylor Reece,

334
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:49,280
