We're looking for
an employee of WellZyn's.

347
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:20,720
Male with a severely damaged ear.

348
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:26,440
Yes. Full disclosure,
that does raise a flag.

349
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:35,560
That's Stan Potolsky.

350
