352
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:44,760
Shampoos, toothpastes.

353
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,840
So what happened?

354
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:50,200
Well, Stan was frustrated that
he wasn't doing more important work.

355
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:53,160
