420
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,040
What story is that?

421
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:10,680
Oh, you better know what story,
my friend.

422
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:13,440
Because if you tell me
the same story he told me,

423
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,360
then I could believe it's true.

424
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:17,240
Then I'm happy.

425
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:20,680
But if you tell me another story,
oh, mama.

426
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:22,720
Then someone's lying to me.

427
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:26,280
And I don't know which one,
and the both of you will die.

428
00:24:26,360 --> 00:24:27,360
Understand?

429
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,160
- Yes, I do.
- Good.

430
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:32,080
So...

431
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:35,320
Tell me a story, Jim.

432
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:41,280
