434
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:44,320
We didn't even know
each other then...

435
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,440
What did I say?

436
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,560
Go put him on the slicer.

437
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,400
No, no, no.

438
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:53,640
If I don't like what I hear,
slice his face prejute.

439
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:56,800
Oh, I'm sorry. Go on.

440
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,160
I was a pawn...

441
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:05,040
in a conspiracy

442
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:08,840
between Falcone,
the mayor and the G.C.P.D.

443
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:11,840
