for the Wayne murders...

444
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:15,920
with the help of Fish Mooney,
Mr. Cobblepot's employer at the time.

445
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:20,360
Mr. Cobblepot then told
the whole story to the MCU.

446
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:25,680
To prove that I wouldn't
betray the conspiracy,

447
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:27,480
Falcone ordered me to kill Cobblepot.

448
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:31,400
I didn't do it.

449
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,400
I let him live.

450
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:37,000
And here we are.

451
00:25:43,600 --> 00:25:46,600
Falcone, Mooney, the MCU cops...

452
00:25:48,040 --> 00:25:49,080
none of them know he's alive?

453
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,200
If they did, I'd be dead already.

454
00:25:57,600 --> 00:25:58,600
It's delicious.

455
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:02,920
Frankie!
Bring the Penguin back out here.

456
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:04,360
The little punk is telling the truth.

457
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:06,520
Thank you, Jim.

458
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:09,040
Good story. Told well.

459
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:11,280
Lot of guys in your situation,
they freak out.

460
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:16,920
There you are, you rat, you snitch,
