462
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:19,920
Be happy, Frankie.

463
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:22,160
We just got a brand-new weapon
against the Falcones.

464
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,840
It's Christmas!

465
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,680
Happy holidays. Can I go now?

466
00:26:25,760 --> 00:26:27,120
Oh, yeah. Jim, you can go.

467
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:32,600
You know, just so that we,
understand each other,

468
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:36,040
you know, keep all this hush-hush.

469
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:37,120
Between us pals.

