00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,880
Good. Better.

483
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:23,120
Now, act as if you've caught me
in a lie.

484
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:26,960
Not angry.

485
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:28,880
No. Disappointment.

486
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:32,880
Oh, honey.

487
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:35,520
Oh, honey.

