00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,000
There you go.

489
00:27:38,600 --> 00:27:40,360
Now, about your hair.

490
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:45,120
There you are.

491
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:48,760
Where the hell have you been?

492
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:51,800
Personal business.

493
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,320
You disappear in the middle
of a case,

494
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:54,520
you can't even tell me why?

495
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,360
That's what "personal" means.

496
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:58,560
