I don't want to know your problems.

498
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:03,120
WellZyn sent by Potolsky's stuff.
Grab a box.

499
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:06,640
- Anything useful yet?
- No. Classic geeky loner.

500
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,800
Lived for his work.

501
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:11,560
No wife, no family, no real friends.

